name: Project Rocket Boost
description:
Control Keys: - [Space] to thrust  - [Left] to turn rocket to the left, - [Right] to turn Rocket to the right.  [ESC] to quit 

- 8 short Levels

- Fly your Rocket to reach the landing zone (Yellow)

Credits:

3D Artist, Game Designer, Programmer: Me (Shishi Juugo)
